ured%20wellness%20sessions%20evolved%20into%20a%20safe%20space%20where%20they%20would%20rely%20on%20each%20other%20for%20advice%2C%20support%2C%20and%20perspective.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ECredits%3A%20Prachi%20Saxena%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Prachi%20Saxena%20and%20Shikha%20Pandey%20%E2%80%94%20two%20wellness%20professionals%20in%20their%2040s%20%E2%80%94%20an%20unexpected%20adult%20friendship%20began%20in%20the%20most%20modern%20way%3A%20over%20a%20Facebook%20comment%20thread%20five%20years%20ago!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20our%20friendship%20began%20with%20a%20few%20casual%20exchanges%2C%20we%20both%20intuitively%20felt%20there%20was%20more%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Prachi%2C%20a%20relationship%20therapist%20and%20co-founder%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Emotional%20Wellness%20Initiatives%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20discovered%20that%20Shikha%20was%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F400018%2Fpawga-pets-yoga-adoption-animal-welfare-shelters-in-chennai-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20holistic%20yoga%20coach.%3C%2Fa%3E%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Prachi%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20consistent%20yoga%20practice%2C%20especially%20after%20a%20diabetes%20scare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20reached%20out%2C%20and%20we%20started%20meeting%20thrice%20a%20week%20for%20yoga.%20But%20slowly%2C%20those%20sessions%20turned%20into%20catch-ups%2C%20confession%20corners%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20full-blown%20venting%20sessions.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20realise%20when%20it%20stopped%20being%20about%20just%20yoga%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20structured%20wellness%20sessions%20evolved%20into%20something%20deeper.%20The%20duo%20found%20themselves%20relying%20on%20each%20other%20for%20advice%2C%20support%2C%20and%20perspective.%20They%20were%20connecting%20as%20wom