-online-shopping-30-days-regain-control-productivity-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elittle%20control%20I%20had%20over%20my%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20had%20enrolled%20in%20business%20school%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20I%20would%20help%20my%20dad's%20law%20firm%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20business%20was%20struggling%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20up%20to%20me%20to%20fix%20it.%20From%20an%20early%20age%2C%20I%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20his%20partner%2C%20not%20just%20his%20son.%20That%20meant%20being%20the%20one%20to%20solve%20problems%2C%20build%20marketing%20plans%2C%20create%20websites%2C%20and%20dig%20through%20legal%20documents%20to%20find%20potential%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20followed%20my%20dad's%20mold.%20I%20was%20always%20striving%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftried-to-fix-my-son-ended-learning-something-about-myself-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20ideal%20son%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that%20left%20me%20little%20space%20to%20explore%20my%20passions.%20I%20just%20learned%20how%20to%20be%20what%20everyone%20expected%20of%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20was%2020%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-became-empty-nester-reinvented-life-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edidn't%20know%20who%20I%20was%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20what%20I%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239875352-ff10-4041-b1b9-6cd4a5574e0a%5C%22%3EThat%20hard%20realization%20broke%20something%20in%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20night%2C%20I%20lost%20it%20on%20the%20bathroom%20floor%20of%20my%20aunt's%20house%2C%20sobbing%20quietly%2C%20alone.%20When%20I%20picked%20myself%20up%20and%20looked%20in%20the%20mirror%2C%20I%20barely%20recognized%20myself%2C%20all%20puffy-eyed%20with%20red%20cheeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20that%20night%2C%20something%20finally%20clicked.%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20save%20my%20dad's%20business.%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20stay%20here%20