o%20take%20care%20of%20myself%20in%20the%20same%20ways%20or%20exercise%20at%20the%20same%20intensity%20I%20was%20used%20to%20anymore%2C%20and%20I%20started%20to%20look%20for%20new%20ways%20of%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20have%20chronic%20fatigue%2C%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20get%20movement%20in%20every%20day%2C%20but%20my%20doctors%20have%20told%20me%20it's%20still%20vital%20to%20try.%20The%20key%20is%20finding%20something%20that%20doesn't%20push%20beyond%20your%20threshold%20but%20also%20keeps%20you%20as%20active%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20go%20walking%20in%20spring%20and%20fall.%20However%2C%20in%20Southern%20Illinois%2C%20where%20I%20live%2C%20temperatures%20and%20weather%20conditions%20in%20summer%20and%20winter%20are%20too%20extreme%20for%20me%20to%20walk%20outside.%20But%20there's%20a%20gym%20with%20a%20pool%20down%20the%20street%2C%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctors-explain-why-people-feel-better-near-the-ocean-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elove%20being%20in%20the%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20look%20at%20their%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271f8aa5a-ca5c-4f18-98fb-2c29e72d968e%5C%22%3EI%20was%20the%20youngest%20person%20in%20the%20class%20by%20a%20few%20decades%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20variety%20of%20pool%20courses%20offered.%20However%2C%20many%20of%20them%20looked%20too%20vigorous.%20The%20only%20ones%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20within%20the%20scope%20of%20my%20abilities%20were%20for%20older%20adults.%20Still%2C%20I%20put%20aside%20my%20self-consciousness%20about%20being%2039%20and%20considering%20this%20particular%20class%2C%20and%20looked%20at%20the%20time%20slots.%20This%20was%20the%20next%20hurdle%20%E2%80%94%20most%20were%20morning%20classes%2C%20as%20older%20people%20are%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwake-up-early-morning-routine-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blan