0give%20me%20more%20freedom%20and%20independence%2C%20and%20make%20my%20life%20easier.%20No%20more%20pulling%20up%20Google%20Maps%20to%20look%20for%20routes%20with%20bike%20lanes%20or%20hitching%20rides%20with%20friends%20and%20feeling%20guilty%20about%20not%20being%20able%20to%20return%20the%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20while%20since%20I've%20been%20in%20the%20car-buying%20game%2C%20and%20I%20quickly%20learned%20that%20I'm%20not%20cut%20out%20for%20it.%20Sitting%20in%20dealership%20offices%2C%20waiting%20as%20sales%20reps%20leave%20to%20go%20%26quot%3Btalk%20to%20their%20manager%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Brun%20the%20numbers%2C%26quot%3B%20only%20to%20return%20with%20news%20that%20the%20sticker%20price%20had%20jumped%20by%20multiple%20Ks%2C%20left%20me%20feeling%20defeated%20and%20convinced%20I%20was%20getting%20ripped%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20this%20%2428%2C000%20Subaru%20I%20test-drove%20became%20a%20nearly%20%2437%2C000%20Subaru%20after%20taxes%2C%20fees%2C%20and%20mysterious%20charges%20like%20%26quot%3Bcpo%20gold%20plus%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcombo%204-1.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222934%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22subaru%20elkins%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688af39d3d5881a51c1e530d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221761%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20weeks%20of%20dealership%20visits%20and%20growing%20indecision%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20throw%20in%20the%20towel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20along%20came%20a%20car%20well%20within%20my%20budget%20that%20ticked%20all%20of%20my%20boxes%20and%20then%20some.%20It%20was%20a%20deal%20that%20was%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%20%E2%80%94%20because%2C%20well%2C%20it%20was%20my%20brother's%20car.%20He%20and%20his%20family%20were%20moving%20from%20Charlotte%20to%20London%20and%20selling%20his%202019%20BMW.%20He%20gave%20me%20the%20generous%20%26quot%3Byounger%20sibling%20discount%26quot%3B%20and%20offered%200%25%20financing%20if%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20it%20all%20in%20one%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20have%20to%20ship%20the%20car%20across%20the%20country%20to%20LA%2C%20but%20besides%20that%2C%20I%20seemed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20sidestep%20many%20hidden%20dealership%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20paid%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20the%20%2416%2C000%20I%20transferred%20to%20my%20brother%2C%20and%20my%20monthly%20expenses%20are%20about%20to%20jump%20in%20a%20way%20that%20has%20me%20playing%20Tetris%20with%20my%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20I%20paid%20for%20besides%20the%20car%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShipping%3A%20%241%2C195.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20one's%20unique%20to%20my%20situation%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20curious%2C%20I%20paid%20RoadRunner%20Auto%20Transport%20%241%2C195.%20I%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20recommend%20top%20car%20transport%20services%2C%20received%20quotes%20from%20five%20companies%2C%20and%20selected%20the%20most%20economical.%20RoadRunner%20picked%20up%20the%20car%20in%20Charlotte%20and%2C%20six%20days%20later%2C%20dropped%20it%20off%20right%20outside%20my%20apartment%20in%20Santa%20Monica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elkins%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688a84533d5881a51c1e4e86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20just%20six%20days%20in%20transit%2C%20my%20car%20arrived%20in%20LA%20from%20the%20east%20coast.%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20tires%3A%20%241%2C700.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20expense%20is%20also%20unique%20to%20my%20situation%2C%20but%20buying%20a%20used%20car%20could%20require%20purchasing%20new%20components.%20I%20paid%20%241%2C700%20for%20four%20new%20tires%20to%20be%20installed.%20If%20that%20sounds%20like%20a%20lot%2C%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20it%20is.%20Four%20regular%20tires%20would%20have%20cost%20me%20closer%20to%20%241%2C000%20to%20install%20and%20align%2C%20but%20I%20was%20advised%20to%20get%20%26quot%3Brun-flat%20tires%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20car%20doesn't%20accommodate%20a%20spare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20companies%20quoted%20me%20about%20%241%2C700%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20the%20price%20was%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmog%20test%3A%20%2476.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20California%2C%20smog%20inspections%20are%20required%20for%20most%20vehicles%20when%20you%20register.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20a%20smog%20check%20station%20about%2010%20minutes%20from%20my%20apartment%20and%20arrived%20promptly%20at%20opening.%20The%20inspection%20took%20just%2015%20minutes.%20While%20waiting%2C%20I%20Googled%20%26quot%3Bcost%20of%20smog%20tests%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20preparing%20to%20shell%20out%20between%20%2430%20and%20%2460.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attendant%20handed%20over%20papers%20confirming%20that%20my%20car%20passed%20the%20test%20and%20a%20%2476%20bill.%20I%20was%20frustrated%20until%20I%20called%20another%20smog%20check%20station%20in%20my%20area%20out%20of%20curiosity.%20They%20quoted%20me%20%2485.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegistration%20fees%3A%20%24282.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20to%20expect%20regarding%20this%20category%2C%20but%20I%20budgeted%20around%20%241%2C000.%20I%20severely%20overestimated%2C%20and%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20when%20I%20left%20my%20DMV%20appointment%20with%20new%20plates%2C%20registration%20stickers%2C%20and%20a%20%24282%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elkins%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688aef833d5881a51c1e52dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20outside%20the%20DMV%20and%20looking%20unprepared%20for%20her%20monthly%20expenses%20to%20jump%20significantly.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFront%20license%20plate%20bracket%3A%20%24108.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECalifornia%20is%20one%20of%20the%2029%20states%20that%20require%20a%20front%20license%20plate%20to%20be%20displayed%20on%20vehicles.%20I%20spent%20%24108%20on%20a%20STO%20N%20SHO%20license%20plate%20bracket%20that's%20compatible%20with%20my%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paid%20an%20additional%20%243%2C361%20on%20top%20of%20my%20brother's%20price.%20But%20the%20additional%20costs%20don't%20end%20there.%20My%20monthly%20expenses%20are%20about%20to%20increase%20by%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECar%20insurance%3A%20%2475%20a%20month.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20spent%20about%20an%20hour%20researching%20insurance%20companies%20and%20requesting%20quotes.%20The%20most%20basic%20coverage%20in%20California%20would%20run%20me%20about%20%2455%2C%20while%20a%20standard%20package%20was%20in%20the%20%24200%20to%20%24250%20range.%20I%20went%20basic%20with%20a%20few%20add-ons%20and%20now%20owe%20USAA%20%2475%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGas%3A%20%2475%20a%20month.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGas%20is%20super%20expensive%20in%20California%2C%20pushing%20%245%20a%20gallon.%20I'm%20not%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20empty%20light%20coming%20on%2C%20and%20I%20expect%20to%20pay%20between%20%2450%20and%20%24100%20per%20month%20to%20refill%20the%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EParking%2C%20maintenance%2C%20and%20miscellaneous%20expenses.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20can%20park%20on%20the%20street%20in%20my%20neighborhood%20for%20free%2C%20but%20it%20wouldn't%20surprise%20me%20if%20I%20racked%20up%20some%20parking%20tickets%20for%20forgetting%20about%20weekly%20street%20sweeping%2C%20which%20costs%20%2473%20per%20offense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20oil%20changes%20to%20keep%20up%20with%2C%20as%20well%20as%20general%20car%20maintenance.%20I've%20been%20warned%20that%20BMWs%20are%20known%20for%20being%20expensive%20to%20maintain