nto%20a%20clean%2C%20green%20stretch%3F%20The%20answer%20lies%20in%20one%20man%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20Environmentalist%20Vikrant%20Tongad%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Noida-based%20non-profit%20organisation%20SAFE%20(Social%20Action%20for%20Forest%20and%20Environment)%2C%20decided%20to%20take%20on%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20worked%20on%20a%20similar%20problem%20in%20Ghaziabad%20earlier%2C%20Vikrant%20was%20no%20stranger%20to%20such%20challenges.%20When%20residents%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20for%20help%2C%20he%20visited%20the%20site%20several%20times.%20The%20reality%20was%20grim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20land%20was%20burdened%20with%20waste%20and%20remnants%20of%20illegal%20soil%20mining.%20There%20were%20uneven%20pits%20as%20deep%20as%20six%20to%20eight%20feet.%20The%20air%20hung%20heavy%20with%20toxic%20fumes%20from%20open%20garbage%20burning%2C%20which%20threatened%20the%20health%20of%20nearby%20residents.%20Concerns%20about%20respiratory%20problems%2C%20especially%20among%20asthma%20patients%2C%20were%20rampant%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20troubled%20the%20local%20community%20most%20was%20the%20potential%20fate%20looming%20over%20their%20heads.%20They%20feared%20this%20site%20could%20turn%20into%20a%20replica%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20infamous%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20%E2%80%94%20an%20environmental%20catastrophe%20that%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20mountain%20of%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20project%20involved%20clearing%2012%20truckloads%20of%20waste%20and%20recycling%201%2C600%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20into%20benches.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetteri