ack%20nutrients%2C%20Darlapudi%20discovered.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20aside%20from%20teaching%20him%20the%20nuances%20of%20green%20farming%20practices%2C%20the%20course%20also%20fuelled%20his%20interest%20in%20the%20ethnoscience%20of%20seeds.%C2%A0%20He%20ventured%20into%20the%20jungles%20of%20Dantewada%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%C2%A0to%20collect%20sample%20seed%20varieties%20grown%20by%20the%20tribal%20communities%20in%20the%20region.%20These%20held%20a%20special%20draw.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20days%2C%20chemical%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides%20are%20used%20in%20agriculture.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20seeds%20get%20diversified%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20But%20in%20these%20tribal%20areas%2C%20he%20found%20the%20seeds%20to%20be%20untouched%20by%20chemicals.%20From%20a%20passion%20trip%2C%20this%20spiralled%20into%20a%20project%20that%20has%20now%20been%20running%20for%20almost%20a%20decade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20not%20all%2C%20he%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20also%20followed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255272%2Fnekram-sharma-nau-anaj-intercropping-system-himachal-pradesh-mandi-traditional-farming-no-fertiliser-millet-cultivation-success-story-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintercropping%20on%20my%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20I%20have%20horticulture%20crops%2C%20intercrops%2C%20green%20vegetables%2C%20and%20leafy%20vegetables.%20I%20have%20also%20introduced%20micro%20irrigation%20and%20drip%20irrigation%20to%20create%20awareness%20about%20saving%20water.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-7_11zon-1732015071.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darlapudi%20trains%20fa