ural%20calamities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20over%20300%20farmers%20in%20seed%20preservation%20techniques.%20But%2C%20the%20legacy%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F176277%2Fkarnataka-bengaluru-organic-farming-native-seeds-woman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseed%20preservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20region%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20with%20him%2C%20he%20insists.%20It%20needs%20to%20be%20an%20ongoing%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20Darlapudi%20Ravi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiucn.org%2Fpress-release%2F202410%2Fmore-one-three-tree-species-worldwide-faces-extinction-iucn-red-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20one%20in%20three%20tree%20species%20worldwide%20faces%20extinction%20%E2%80%93%20IUCN%20Red%20List%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20IUCN%2C%20Published%20on%2028%20October%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsii.in%2Fimportance-of-seed-banks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImportance%20of%20Seed%20Banks%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Federation%20of%20Seed%20Industry%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753965000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-2-1732015773.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D479175%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Darlapudi%20Ravi%20was%20an%20assistant%20general%20manager%20at%20a%20cement%20industry%20when%20he%20realised%20how%20m