%80%94%20in%20words%20people%20use%20every%20day.%20The%20focus%20is%20on%20conversations%20driven%20by%20communities%20themselves%2C%20not%20imposed%20from%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753884580.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nirakar%20Behera%20raises%20awareness%20about%20ecosystem%20conservation%20and%20mangrove%20reforestation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753884580.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753884580-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753884580-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753884580-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753884580-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-478545%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENirakar%20Behera%20raises%20awareness%20about%20ecosystem%20conservation%20and%20mangrove%20reforestation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20the%20joint%20idea%20of%20a%20situated%20economy%20and%20a%20place-based%20approach%20along%20with%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devjit%20Mittra%2C%20Executive%20Director%20of%20Socratus%20Foundation%20in%20India%2C%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20look%20for%20anchors%20in%20each%20place%20%E2%80%94%20people%20already%20trusted%20by%20the%20community%2C%20like%20Nirakar%20or%20Madhusmit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20through%20them%2C%20we%20