e%20people.%20Nearly%2023%20percent%20of%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20population%20belongs%20to%2064%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20Twelve%20out%20of%20its%2030%20districts%20are%20tribal-dominated%2C%20home%20to%20communities%20living%20across%20forests%2C%20wetlands%2C%20farmlands%2C%20and%20coastal%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20its%20philosophy%20to%20life%2C%20Socratus%20teamed%20up%20with%20organisations%20like%20Sambad%20and%20Bakul%20Foundation%20and%20launched%20the%20Climate%20Panchayat%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-500x855.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20colourful%20maps%20of%20Odisha%20showing%20groundwater%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20extreme%20weather%20trends.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-500x855.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-175x300.jpg%20175w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-768x1314.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-898x1536.jpg%20898w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-150x257.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935.jpg%20988w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-478542%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sessions%20bring%20together%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20of%20a%20locality%20%E2%80%94%20men%2C%20women%2C%20farmers%2C%20forest%20workers%2C%20youth%2C%20scientists%2C%20and%20even%20MLAs%20sometimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Devjit.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20gets%20a%20chance%20to%20share%20grievances%2C%20ideas%2C%20and%20solutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meetings%20are%20organised%20around%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20147%20legislative%20constituencies%20%E2%80%94%20a%20conscious%20choice%20to%20match%20political%20boundaries%20and%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20track%20progress.%20The%20larger%20vision%3F%20To%20turn%20Climate%20Panchayat%20into%20a%20governance%20tool%20that%20can%20work%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocratus%20also%20facilitates%20other%20gatherings%2C%20such%20as%20Gram%20Swabhiman%20(in%20collaboration%20with%20Goonj%20and%20Nature%E2%80%99s%20Club)%2C%20where%20only%20community%20members%20come%20together%20to%20rebuild%20confidence%20and%20ownership%20over%20their%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20launch%2C%20152%20Climate%20Panchayats%20and%2048%20Gram%20Swabhiman%20meetings%20have%20been%20held.%20Over%2010%2C000%20citizens%20have%20participated%20directly%2C%20while%20more%20than%20two%20lakh%20people%20have%20engaged%20through%20Sambad%E2%80%99s%20print%2C%20digital%2C%20and%20social%20media.%20The%20impact%20is%20visible%20%E2%80%94%20insights%20from%20these%20conversations%20have%20already%20reached%20the%20Odisha%20Assembly%2C%20with%2020%20MLAs%20raising%20climate%20issues%20based%20on%20what%20communities%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Community%20meetings%20in%20Bhitarkanika%20give%20families%20a%20platform%20to%20plan%20solutions%20to%20local%20climate%20challenges.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.