o%20prioritise%20issues%20like%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20sanitation%2C%20and%20safety%20%E2%80%93%20sectors%20that%20directly%20impact%20the%20most%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20Bengal%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20this%20shift%20is%20already%20visible.%20From%20faster%20grievance%20redressal%20to%20more%20inclusive%20implementation%20of%20schemes%2C%20district-level%20officers%20are%20setting%20a%20new%20benchmark%20for%20public%20service%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20ahead%3A%20Building%20on%20this%20momentum%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20is%20worth%20celebrating%2C%20it%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20benchmark%20for%20other%20states.%20The%20journey%20ahead%20is%20not%20just%20about%20recruiting%20more%20women%20into%20the%20IAS%20but%20ensuring%20they%20are%20supported%2C%20heard%2C%20and%20given%20room%20to%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20narrow%20bylanes%20of%20Prayagraj%20to%20the%20maternity%20ward%20in%20Kerala%20and%20the%20quiet%20resilience%20of%20a%20Baroda%20graduate%2C%20the%20journeys%20of%20Shakti%20Dubey%2C%20Malavika%20G%20Nair%2C%20and%20Harshita%20Goyal%20offer%20a%20compelling%20portrait%20of%20what%20it%20means%20to%20persevere%20with%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakti%20Dubey%2C%20who%20secured%20the%20All%20India%20Rank%201%20in%20the%20UPSC%202024%20exam%2C%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20police%20officer%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Her%20achievement%20is%20not%20only%20a%20testament%20to%20her%20academic%20brilliance%20but%20also%20a%20reflection%20of%20her%20grounded%20upbringing%20and%20the%20values%20instilled%20in%20her%20by%20a%20family%20steeped%20in%20public%20service.%20With%20her%20feet%20firmly%20planted%20and%20her%20eyes%20set%20on%20impactful%20change%2C%20Shakti%20is%20poised%20to%20be%20a%20dynamic%20force%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20civil%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%