%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F384890%2Fmerino-industries-water-conservation-water-management-ponds-reservoirs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20harvesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20conservation%20techniques%20that%20are%20tailored%20to%20fit%20the%20unique%20geographical%20and%20cultural%20needs%20of%20the%20place%20and%20the%20community%20inhabiting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20World%20Water%20Day%20we%20pledged%20to%20delve%20into%20the%20pages%20of%20history%20and%20highlight%20some%20of%20the%20significant%20sustainable%20water%20conservation%20methods%20practised%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAhar%20Pynes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%20wp-image-280153%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1648033853.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ahars%20are%20used%20for%20irrigation%20during%20dry%20months%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1648033853.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1648033853-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1648033853-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1648033853-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1648033853-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-280153%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAhars%20are%20used%20for%20irrigation%20during%20dry%20months.%20Picture%20Credits%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiawaterportal.o